      About this item

      • 2.4GHz Wi-Fi Compatible Connects to 2.4GHz networks of single-, dual- and tri-band routers through effortless pairing options for use with the latest home Wi-Fi equipment. DOES NOT WORK WITH 5GHz NETWORKS.
      • Voice Control No hub required for voice commands through Amazon Alexa and Google Assistant.
      • Easy-to-Use App Versatile UltraPro app available in the Apple App Store and Google Play simplifies network connection for hassle-free mobile operation of lights, fans and more. Alerts and do-not-disturb function allow personalized monitoring without inconvenient interruptions.
      • Simple Setup Schedules and automations support full customization based on times, presets, weather, location and other factors. Organize devices by rooms and homes to control several locations from one app.
      • Heavy-Duty Design 2 simultaneously controlled outlets and weather-resistant construction withstand the elements.

      From the manufacturer

      Automate your appliances

      Automate and control outdoor lighting, holiday dcor, water features and more from anywhere with a mobile device.

      One-step schedules.

      Automations.

      Simple presets.

      Manual ON/OFF operation.

      Full-range countdown.

      Groups.

      No hub necessary

      Required

      2.4GHz Wi-Fi network dual- and tri-band router compatible.

      Control at your fingertips UltraPro app

      Enjoy easy set up and control via the UltraPro app.

      The app is free and available in the Apple App Store (iOS) and Google Play (Android).

      Search "UltraPro."

      TIP: Download and create your account while your device ships.

      Turn ON/OFF connected devices, create schedules, activate automations, trigger countdowns, set up groups and more through the app.

      Voice control Amazon Alexa & Hey Google compatible

      Whether you are carrying a load of laundry, left your phone in another room or simply dont want to leave the couch, hands-free control is the ideal solution. Voice commands allow you to control UltraPro Wi-Fi products without lifting a finger.

      "Alexa, turn ON landscape lights."

      "Hey Google, turn OFF Christmas decorations."

      Amazon certified for voice control with Alexa devices enabled via the Alexa app

      Google Assistant enabled via the Google Home app

      Daily or weekly schedules

      Create schedules for every part of your life.

      Workdays.

      Weekends.

      School.

      Workouts.

      Vacations.

      Holidays and more.

      Self-adjusts to your area

      As dusk and dawn times for your location change, sunset and sunrise automations adjust your schedules. No longer reprogram your device to accommodate ever-changing daylight times throughout the year.

      ON/OFF operation

      Smart devices turn ON and OFF with the press of a button.

      Remote control from your mobile device anywhere you have an internet connection.

      Manual button on the smart switch if internet or your mobile device is unavailable.

      Full-range countdown

      Program a countdown to turn ON or OFF the smart switch from one minute up to 24 hours.

      If a device is ON when the countdown is activated, the connected light turns OFF when the countdown expires. When the countdown is initiated with the smart device OFF, it turns ON at the end of the set time.

      Main Screen

      Immediately upon opening the app, control, add and manage devices. Convenient tabs provide quick access to other beneficial features.

      Plus symbol add devices to your network.

      Power icon turn ON (green) or turn OFF (gray) individual devices with a tap.

      Home return to the main screen from any tab.

      Groups organize and manage collections of devices to operate simultaneously.

      Automations create and edit programs for devices and groups through sunset/sunrise times, weather, location and more.

      Support access FAQs, how-to videos, account information, settings and more.

      Preset and custom schedules

      Quickly activate or deactivate and customize preset programs for your needs.

      Pick your desired ON/OFF times, specific day(s) for the schedule, select weekly for a reoccurring schedule or once for an individual program.

      Presets evening, morning, dust-to-dawn and countdown options quickly schedule common programs.

      Grouping devices

      Conveniently group two or more devices for control on the same schedule or through simultaneous ON/OFF operation from the app.

      Create groups for areas of your home or activities:

      Bedroom.

      Backyard.

      Kitchen.

      Living room.

      Patio.

      Reading.

      Movie nights.

      Dinner and more.

      Support

      The support tab provides account information and useful resources about the UltraPro app and Wi-Fi devices.

      Home management create and edit locations to organize, monitor and manage devices from one account.

      Message center stores alerts about device status, account activity and more.

      FAQ and feedback links to frequently asked questions addressing common topics for full use of your Wi-Fi devices.

      App settings access account information, notification preferences, app details and more.

      Amazon Alexa/Google Home provides instructions for linking the UltraPro app to smart speakers for voice control.

      Product Description

      Enjoy professional automation with DIY ease from the UltraPro Outdoor Plug-in Wi-Fi Smart Switch. Connect the smart switch to a 2.4GHz Wi-Fi network to control and schedule plug-in landscape lights, seasonal dcor and other outdoor devices. By supporting dual- and tri-band routers, the device is ideal for the latest equipment. The easy-to-use Enbrighten app with diverse, hassle-free pairing options is available on the Apple App Store and Google Play. Direct compatibility with Amazon Alexa and Google Assistant supports convenient voice commands without a hub. Creating a lighting program from anywhere has never been simpler. The switch works with all bulb types and features two simultaneously controlled grounded outlets with weather-resistant covers as well as a manual ON/OFF button. To fully automate your life, connected equipment is controlled by scheduled settings, weather changes, location and full-range countdowns. Custom ON/OFF commands support operation around the clock while preset automations allow lighting control at the perfect time of day. Smart is simple with the UltraPro Outdoor Plug-in Wi-Fi Smart Switch.

      How customer reviews and ratings work

      Customer Reviews, including Product Star Ratings help customers to learn more about the product and decide whether it is the right product for them.

      To calculate the overall star rating and percentage breakdown by star, we dont use a simple average. Instead, our system considers things like how recent a review is and if the reviewer bought the item on Amazon. It also analyzed reviews to verify trustworthiness.

      4 out of 5 stars
      Worked perfectly after a little hiccup on setup; Alexa all the way!
      This "UltraPro Outdoor Smart Plug" is well built, designed for the outdoor. It has 2 outlets, but they are NOT individually controllable; it is either BOTH ON, or BOTH OFF. You would need to download and use the "UltraPro" app on your phone to set this smart plug up. And if you home wifi has a "password" (like most people would these days), you would need to setup this plug with "manual setup" and then "manual mode" (and you would need to push the button on the plug to reset the plug one or two times until the blue light is blinking SLOWLY). Anyways, all of these are in the instructions (in the app), they are just not the most straightforward or the easiest to follow if you are unsure about what to look for.After you successfully get the smart plug connected to your UltraPro app, you can go to your Alexa app, and add the "UltraPro Skill"; then from this point on, you will never need to use the UltraPro app, you can directly use Alexa to turn ON and OFF this outdoor smart plug.I set mine up in the backyard to turn ON and OFF some outdoor string lighting, it had been working flawlessly. I use Alexa to automate them to turn ON and OFF at certain times too. The construction of it looks sturdy and seems to be able to withstand the outdoor.Thank you for reading this review, I hoped that this review & the pictures are helpful to you in support of your purchase decision.

      • Trusted Reviewer
        4.0 out of 5 stars Good for automating your holiday lights.
        Reviewed in the United States on December 7, 2020
        Size: 1 PackColor: Outdoor Dual OutletAmazon Vine Customer Review of Free Product( What's this? )
        This is a good, basic, outdoor, WiFi smart plug that works as expected and a great option for automating outdoor holiday or patio lights.

        The product arrived packaged in an easy to open cardboard box that included only this smart plug and a small instruction pamphlet. The build quality of the plug is good enough (I'm not disappointed), but I own another outdoor smart plug (same form-factor and features) that is higher quality, although it was also more expensive.

        Setup is very straight forward, simply scan the QR code included in the instructions to find and download the appropriate app to your device, create an account and follow the instructions. I did have to manually enter my WiFi information (ssid and password), but once I did it came online right away.

        You can manually control power with a button on the plug or you can control remotely using the app. The app is clean, simple and intuitive. Using the app you can create and control lighting groups (if you have more devices from this same manufacture), create automations, or simply setup on/off timers. Amazon Alexa support is also pretty straight forward, within the app you select "Support", then "Connect to Amazon Alexa" and link your account.

        There are a few area this falls short. First, the instructions say to scan the QR code or search the app store for the "UltraPro" app. I was unable to find an "UltraPro" app in the Apple app store and scanning the QR code directs me to an app called "enbrighten" which creates a little confusion. Also, there's no support for integration with Samsung Smartthing or any other smarthome hub other than Google/Amazon.

        One thing to consider when purchasing these WiFi smart devices (plugs/switches/lights/etc.) is that you have to create an online account for each different manufacture you use. So from an account management/security prospective, it's wise to stick to a single trusted brand rather than having to create an online account with several different companies.

        It's also worth noting that this operates on 2.4Ghz WiFi only, which is common for many outdoor WiFi devices because while 2.4Ghz signals offer less bandwidth, they offer greater range and penetration of exterior walls. Plus you don't need much bandwidth to trigger a switch.

        Overall, I think this is a good option for controlling outdoor, seasonal holiday lighting, but for everyday needs there better options available. Although, you may pay a little more.
